                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " Esfahbod is one of the authors of Harfbuzz. This project is about a decade old, and the performance is eclipsed by modern work, such as Raph Levien's Piet (research project) and Pathfinder (which is production quality)."
                            }
